{"title":"收发式主任","authors":["易和元"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":2,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"收发式主任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁 聪画  易和元诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阁下大才真不差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批阅公文是专家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天办公两件事："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收收发发收收发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大事上级作指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小事下级具体抓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的干脆往外转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的作废画叉叉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保险柜里把官作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠然自得谁不夸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜贵体多康泰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心跳正好六十八！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}